{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And their function was like a public fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went out with the fire truck to surrounding towns and villages, and they fought fires.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're all Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I sort of said to the guard, I want to go to the fire brigade because I hear they want-- they called it PIPL-- P-I-P-L.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To be a PIPL went like, like a batman, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I go up to the fire brigade and I talk to one of these firemen, and he says yes, you can be my PIPL.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he immediately organized the bunk for me and gave me some food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was again in this situation where a grown-up was helping me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there were about four or five boys like that in this fire brigade thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fire brigade barrack in Mauthausen was right at the main gate of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The main gate of the camp was sort of granite big gate with towers on either side like a castle, granite walls with wire above.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you couldn't see out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once you were in the camp in Mauthausen, you couldn't see out because of the walls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So again, I had this feeling of, you know, being closed in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then these other boys, they were all masturbating with each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they immediately wanted me to participate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I demurred-- oh, I have to tell you, the block next to ours, next to the fire brigade block, was the bordello.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a camp bordello in Mauthausen which had Jewish women in it, not German women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the fire brigade, every time they went to fight a fire, they'd get so many tickets.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
